author: claude-code-agent
parent: pm-m2u1
resolution: "Adopted: actionability is a pure corpus function — ready = active leaf with no open blocked_by; containers (open descendants) excluded; recommended = top READY by compareCriticalItems (in-progress first). Implemented in pm-nj90."
expected_result: "A documented, schema-agnostic readiness model reusing the existing blocked_by resolver and criticality comparator, with no type allowlist."
actual_result: Implemented in core/item/actionability.ts (computeActionabilityReport) and consumed by pm next; collectBlockedByIds shared with close.ts; compareCriticalItems/collectSubtreeIds promoted to public context.ts exports.
close_reason: "Decision implemented by pm-nj90: dependency-aware actionability (ready = active leaf with no open blocked_by; containers excluded; recommended = top READY by compareCriticalItems, in-progress first). collectBlockedByIds extracted to core/item/actionability.ts as the single source of truth shared with close.ts auto-unblock; compareCriticalItems/collectSubtreeIds promoted to public context.ts exports. Shipped and verified."
